Interface TypeConverter<TO_TYPE,DOMAIN_TYPE>

  • Type Parameters:
    TO_TYPE - type in transfer object
    DOMAIN_TYPE - type in domain object
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractListTypeConverter, AbstractSetTypeConverter, AbstractToDomainTypeConverter, AutomaticListTypeConverter, AutomaticSetTypeConverter, AutomaticStringEnumTypeConverter, DateDateMidnightConverter, DateDateTimeConverter, ListTypeConverter, MappedBy.DefaultTypeConverter, NoConversionTypeConverter, ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticListTypeConverter, ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticSetTypeConverter, ReadOnlyDomainAutomaticTypeConverter, ReadOnlyDomainListTypeConverter, ReadOnlyDomainTypeConverter, SetTypeConverter, StringEnumTypeConverter, ToDomainTypeConverter

    public interface TypeConverter<TO_TYPE,DOMAIN_TYPE>
    Do type conversion to allow object to be stored using a different type in transfer and domain objects.
